{"tid":1604624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個福建中學嘅學生(代po)","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:57:26.000Z","uid":259422,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2c93762db8e358c925bd5df7e91950c24da578fa","tid":1604624,"uid":259422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"我係一個福建中學嘅學生。<br />\n眾所周知福建係一間紅到仆街嘅學校。<br />\n我哋今日全日都係慶祝國慶嘅活動。<br />\n於是就有一d哥哥姐姐自發性係今日升旗典禮完嗰時嗌口號。<br />\n佢哋只不過係一班十幾歲嘅00後學生。但係佢哋就算冇大台同埋會比學校秋後算賬都係都肯企出嚟，係支那嗰支旗同校長面前嗌口號。<br />\n各位連登嘅哥哥姐姐可唔可以應承我哋，聽日企出嚟，唔好辜負我哋呢班00後嘅心願。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n香港人加油<br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係觀塘嗰間 唔係小西灣嗰間</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2c9d64cd46977be01808cdf45777c8d4696c5b3a","tid":1604624,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"gchi ching"},{"pid":"89da66f3708c1c3c7792b45c2cedc3af37324bdf","tid":1604624,"uid":259422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"本人係P牌仔推唔郁 求ching幫推"},{"pid":"452782fb9a3135da0a5b9be4c23f0fda34601d86","tid":1604624,"uid":259422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR8xAo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR8xAo3.jpg&h=49058804&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a40cdb0eca6deae0739afda69b98654b45bb21bb","tid":1604624,"uid":259422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31be2a2d199a24bacdea31f46c3eb0150565fea","t